## Overview

This guide walks you through setting up **VRseBuilder MCP** on:

- **OpenCode Terminal UI (Mandatory)**
- OpenCode Desktop UI (Optional) (Userfriendly + Little buggy and slow)
- OpenChamber (Optional) (Userfriendly)
- **Unity (VRseBuilder Unity MCP plugin) (Mandatory)**

---

## Desktop setup (OpenCode)

