1. Download and run: [opencode-setup.exe](https://autovrse-my.sharepoint.com/:u:/g/personal/venkat_swaraj_autovrse_in/IQBnrsu3XKzrRogRNKX7pa2tAUkANYTsWgV9zFNZjj1kb94?e=5tTKW6)
